library(tidyverse)
library(caret)
library(rpart)
library(rpart.plot)

Regression Trees пакета rpart

Пример с функцией

X <- seq(-2, 2, 0.5)
y <- X^3
qplot(X, y)

df <- data.frame(
            x = X,
            y = y
        )
fit <- rpart(y ~ x,
                data = df,
                method = "anova",
                control = rpart.control(
                    minsplit = 4,
                    cp = 0.0001,
                    xval = 5,  # number of cross-validations
                    maxdepth = 3
                )
            )
y_pred <- predict(fit, newdata = data.frame(x = X))
qplot(X, y) + geom_step(aes(X, y_pred))

prp(fit)
